text:
AROMA: sweet, fresh, coriander, a, bit of citrus, yeast;
APPEARANCE: very hazy, color of bright honey, cute white head, very good lacing;
TASTE: sweet, nicely sour, no bitterness, yeast;
PALATE: very high carbonation, medium body;
OVERALL: pleasant, but not gripping. Id prefer lower carbonation and stronger counter to sweetness, however its not square with guidelines of style.
